title: $:/changenotes/5.4.0/problem-center
description: Add centralized runtime problem registry and Problems sidebar tab
release: 5.4.0
tags: $:/tags/ChangeNote
change-type: enhancement
change-category: core

a new centralized runtime problem registry has been added for browser diagnostics.

Highlights:

* new API entrypoint `$tw.reportProblem(...)`
* browser registry object `$tw.problemRegistry`
* snapshot diff helper `$tw.diffProblemSnapshots(...)`
* new sidebar tab [[$:/core/ui/SideBar/Problems]]
* bridge from `logger.alert()` into structured problems
* hook pipe-mode missing-return diagnostics integrated into registry

The feature makes it easier for users and automation tools to detect newly introduced runtime problems.
